almost a week ago.

54
00:04:29,939 --> 00:04:31,975
You mean they just vanished?

55
00:04:32,019 --> 00:04:34,692
GRACE: Into thin air.

56
00:04:34,739 --> 00:04:36,889
No notice, nothing. They didn 't
even collect their wages.

57
00:04:36,939 --> 00:04:39,692
They... they just left us.

58
00:04:39,739 --> 00:04:41,889
MRS MILLS :
what a strange thing to do.

59
00:04:41,939 --> 00:04:43,850
GRACE: You 'll soon find out
there are times...

60
00:04:43,899 --> 00:04:47,255
