much stronger than this.

148
00:09:25,219 --> 00:09:27,369
otherwise,
in a matter of minutes...

149
00:09:27,419 --> 00:09:29,171
they will break out
in sores and blisters...

150
00:09:29,219 --> 00:09:32,336
and begin to suffocate.

151
00:09:32,379 --> 00:09:33,858
It would eventually be fatal.

152
00:09:33,899 --> 00:09:36,129
MRS MILLS : good heavens.

153
00:09:37,139 --> 00:09:38,777
I don 't like this toast.

154
00:09:38,819 --> 00:09:40,377
oh ? why not?

155
00:09:40,419 --> 00:09:42,489
