They're not coming back, child.

160
00:09:54,299 --> 00:09:57,132
Just like Daddy.

161
00:09:57,179 --> 00:09:59,568
Daddy is coming back, though.

162
00:09:59,619 --> 00:10:03,498
Mrs Mills, our father's
fighting in a war in France.

163
00:10:03,539 --> 00:10:04,892
NICHOLAS : It's the world war.

164
00:10:04,939 --> 00:10:06,736
I know, but he 's in France.

165
00:10:06,779 --> 00:10:10,897
That's enough, chatterboxes.
Finish up your breakfasts.

166
00:10:10,939 --> 00:10:14,329
Are you going to leave us, too ?

167
00:10:14,379 --> 00:10:17,655
of course not!

168
00:10:17,699 --> 00:10:19,417
