almost say... unbearable.

217
00:12:43,219 --> 00:12:46,529
The only way of enduring it
is by keeping a cool head.

218
00:12:46,579 --> 00:12:48,774
oh, yes, ma 'am.

219
00:12:48,819 --> 00:12:51,379
I don 't like fantasies.

220
00:12:51,419 --> 00:12:53,694
Strange ideas.
Do you know what I mean ?

221
00:12:53,739 --> 00:12:56,697
I think so, ma 'am.

222
00:12:56,739 --> 00:13:00,527
My children sometimes
have strange ideas.

223
00:13:00,579 --> 00:13:03,252
But you mustn 't pay
any attention to them.

224
00:13:03,299 --> 00:13:06,177
Children will be children.

225
00:13:06,219 --> 00:13:08,494
Yes, of course, ma 'am.

226
00:13:08,539 --> 00:13:13,329
All right. You can stay.

227
00:13:14,819 --> 00:13:17,333
Thank you very much, ma 'am.

228
00:13:28,339 --> 00:13:30,409
It did happen.

229
00:13:40,099 --> 00:13:41,817
NICHOLAS : "The Roman governor
tried to make them...

230
00:13:41,859 --> 00:13:43,611
"change their minds
afterwards... "

231
00:13:43,659 --> 00:13:46,810
"To make them change
their minds. " Full stop.

232
00:13:46,859 --> 00:13:48,770
- "Afterwards... "
-Mm-hmm.

233
00:13:48,819 --> 00:13:50,332
"He ordered them
to be beaten.

234
00:13:50,379 --> 00:13:54,338
"But Justus and Pastor,
far from being afraid...

235
00:13:54,379 --> 00:13:56,813
"rejoiced and showed themselves
willing to die for Christ.

236
00:13:56,859 --> 00:13:58,497
"when he saw this...

237
00:13:58,539 --> 00:14:00,336
"the Roman governor
was filled with rage...

238
00:14:00,379 --> 00:14:01,937
"and ordered their heads
to be cut off. "

239
00:14:01,979 --> 00:14:04,288
[giggles]

240
00:14:05,739 --> 00:14:07,616
[Snickers]

241
00:14:07,659 --> 00:14:10,617
what do you find so amusing?

242
00:14:10,659 --> 00:14:12,058
well...

243
00:14:12,099 --> 00:14:13,976
well, what?

244
00:14:14,019 --> 00:14:16,408
Those children
were really stupid.

245
00:14:16,459 --> 00:14:18,415
why?

246
00:14:18,459 --> 00:14:20,177
Because they said
they only believed in Jesus...

247
00:14:20,219 --> 00:14:22,779
and then
they got killed for it.

248
00:14:22,819 --> 00:14:24,969
And what would you have done,
deny Christ?

249
00:14:25,019 --> 00:14:26,418
ANNE: well, yes.

250
00:14:26,459 --> 00:14:28,290
Inside I would have
believed in him...

251
00:14:28,339 --> 00:14:31,058
but I wouldn 't have told
the ROMANS that.

252
00:14:33,659 --> 00:14:35,570
Is that what you think, too,
Nicholas ?

253
00:14:39,219 --> 00:14:41,494
I see.

254
00:14:41,539 --> 00:14:44,929
So you would have lied
